data.description: Gracious one story home in Lost Creek. Gleaming floors in living and dining rooms and plantation shutters throughout. Formal living and dining room, 2nd living area beyond the formal living room, nicely appointed kitchen with lovely breakfast area and private interior courtyard. Generously sized master suite, 2nd bedroom with private bathroom. 3rd bedroom is currently used as a study and features those gleaming floors and shares a Jack & Jill bathroom with 4th bedroom. Covered patio and garage with incredible storage.  This property is being sold AS-IS!
